P_1(x_1,y_1,z_1)
P_2(x_2,y_2,z_2)
\alpha, \beta, \gamma
\overline{P_1 P_2}
\cos{\alpha}=\frac{\Delta x}{d},\cos{\beta}=\frac{\Delta y}{d},\cos{\gamma}=\frac{\Delta z}{d}
d=\sqrt{(\Delta x)^2+(\Delta y)^2+(\Delta z)^2}
\alpha = \arccos{\frac{\Delta x}{d}}, \beta = \arccos{\frac{\Delta y}{d}}, \gamma = \arccos{\frac{\Delta z}{d}}
